# Mapper policy

## Banned: legacy ForgeMap

Do **not** restore the old `forgemap` Lua plugin, MAP buttons from that experiment, or revive deleted ForgeMap code paths.

- Old profiles may still mention `forgemap` — `PluginParser` skips that plugin; optionally run `scripts/strip_forgemap_from_profile.py`.

## Allowed: new Mapper (`lib/mapper/`)

The user has started a **new** first-party Mapper project (Java UI + thin APIs), documented in the local gitignored plan `docs/MAPPER_V1_PLAN.md`.

- Implement under `com.resurrection.blowtorch2.lib.mapper` (and related UI/commands/settings).
- Work on **`staging`** + **btTest** until an explicit production release is requested.
- Do not reintroduce the old plugin name `forgemap`.
